<geoCoordinate id="42BAD8F6FE60BD56812403C5EE525C14" direction="west" orientation="longitude" precision="925" value="-8.216666">8°13'W</geoCoordinate>
, Fig. 2, locality 1), 10.iv.2010 (pupal stage), S. Korenko leg., adult emerged 12.iv.2010. 1 ♀ Monsaraz, olive grove (
<geoCoordinate id="F06379D2A85FBC39D1C4612409FAEB4A" direction="north" orientation="latitude" precision="925" value="38.433334">38°26' N</geoCoordinate>
