<geoCoordinate id="66CC6ABD52FB1A1F5ED44770136533DB" direction="north" orientation="latitude" precision="925" value="38.2">38°12'N</geoCoordinate>
, 
<geoCoordinate id="48F7892D12FEDB6704F79412BA92BFA5" direction="west" orientation="longitude" precision="925" value="-7.5333333">7°32'W</geoCoordinate>
, Fig. 2, locality 3), 11.iv.2010, S. Korenko leg., larvae on 
<taxonomicName id="015FC788444223E0D08F08C65689D6C0" class="Arachnida" family="Zodariidae" genus="Zodarion" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Zodarion styliferum" order="Araneae" pageId="7" pageNumber="8" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="styliferum">Zodarion styliferum</taxonomicName>
, pupated 14.iv.2010, adults emerged 27.iv.2010 (female) and 28.iv.2010 (male), female escaped.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="810D47847846E34D14039B84661439FD" pageId="7" pageNumber="8">
